lead_paragraph: Vincent Lecavalier tied it with 12.2 seconds remaining in regulation, Marian Gaborik scored in overtime and the Los Angeles Kings rallied past the San Jose Sharks 3-2 Sunday night.

headline.print_headline: Kings Rally Late to Beat Sharks 3-2 in OT
